title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1988-09-18
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger
Franklin's Tower
Never Trust A Woman
Big Railroad Blues
Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again
Stagger Lee
Promised Land

Set 2

Not Fade Away
Scarlet Begonias
Fire On The Mountain
Man Smart (Woman Smarter)
Drums
Space
The Other One
Wharf Rat
Throwing Stones
Not Fade Away

Encore:
Black Muddy River

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
